main event: One to three transparent objects were sighted traveling west over McChord AFB, Washington, on the night of 26-27 August 1966.
interesting points: Witnesses described the objects as resembling a transparent kite and a bi-plane., Objects were visible for about 20-30 minutes., The objects were observed without any sound., No physical evidence was found to support the sighting., The conclusion reached was that the sighting was likely caused by a weather balloon.
